  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/bc82d429177fbd1c83a90c69703e9167.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=260 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/bc82d429177fbd1c83a90c69703e9167.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/bc82d429177fbd1c83a90c69703e9167.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THOSE GAMES are now more challenging and more fun than ever!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play upgraded, harder versions of minigames from THOSE GAMES 1 and 2!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the minigames you know and love, now with a whole new layer of hardcore challenge</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > and replayability!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/740a353b5cab21501909b1138a77982b.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=290 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/740a353b5cab21501909b1138a77982b.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/740a353b5cab21501909b1138a77982b.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THOSE GAMES EXTREME is a new, more challenging THOSE GAMES experience. Enjoy flashier</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > attacks, animations, and stage gimmicks for more excitement and drama than ever!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/abd4ce0d894bde43d5de620e551eb8a9.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=260 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/abd4ce0d894bde43d5de620e551eb8a9.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/abd4ce0d894bde43d5de620e551eb8a9.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring new versions of THOSE GAMES staples, all with updated visuals, including Pin Pull,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Number Tower, Color Lab, Knock-Back Shooter, Draw & Guard, and Spellbinding Scroll (now</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > upgraded to Survival Scroll!).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/0fe9523644b2cf040e7fdb30f8a0aa19.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=296 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/0fe9523644b2cf040e7fdb30f8a0aa19.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/0fe9523644b2cf040e7fdb30f8a0aa19.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for the hardest instalment in the THOSE GAMES series yet? Are you ready...for THOSE GAMES EXTREME?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・A new instalment in the THOSE GAMES series, with a focus on higher difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Features familiar minigames with updated visuals for a fresh new look.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Enjoy bite-sized gaming challenges to your hearts' content, with 155 stages across six different minigames!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Compete against other players from around the world in Rank-Up Challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Use the coins you earn in-game to get plates and titles from the Gotcha! machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Combine plates and titles to create and customize your own Title Plate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・View global leaderboards updated every month in Latest Rankings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Complete a variety of different missions to earn rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*Some minigame stages from THOSE GAMES and THOSE GAMES 2 also appear in this game as tutorial stages.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New players can use these stages to get used to the mechanics before things get too crazy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Or, if you're a THOSE GAMES veteran, skip the tutorial and get right into the extreme action!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Either way, the tutorials will always be there for you, so you can play with confidence!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/bc82d429177fbd1c83a90c69703e9167.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=260 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/bc82d429177fbd1c83a90c69703e9167.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/bc82d429177fbd1c83a90c69703e9167.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THOSE GAMES are now more challenging and more fun than ever!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play upgraded, harder versions of minigames from THOSE GAMES 1 and 2!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the minigames you know and love, now with a whole new layer of hardcore challenge</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > and replayability!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/740a353b5cab21501909b1138a77982b.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=290 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/740a353b5cab21501909b1138a77982b.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/740a353b5cab21501909b1138a77982b.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THOSE GAMES EXTREME is a new, more challenging THOSE GAMES experience. Enjoy flashier</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > attacks, animations, and stage gimmicks for more excitement and drama than ever!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/abd4ce0d894bde43d5de620e551eb8a9.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=260 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/abd4ce0d894bde43d5de620e551eb8a9.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/abd4ce0d894bde43d5de620e551eb8a9.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring new versions of THOSE GAMES staples, all with updated visuals, including Pin Pull,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Number Tower, Color Lab, Knock-Back Shooter, Draw & Guard, and Spellbinding Scroll (now</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > upgraded to Survival Scroll!).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/0fe9523644b2cf040e7fdb30f8a0aa19.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=296 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/0fe9523644b2cf040e7fdb30f8a0aa19.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/0fe9523644b2cf040e7fdb30f8a0aa19.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for the hardest instalment in the THOSE GAMES series yet? Are you ready...for THOSE GAMES EXTREME?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・A new instalment in the THOSE GAMES series, with a focus on higher difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Features familiar minigames with updated visuals for a fresh new look.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Enjoy bite-sized gaming challenges to your hearts' content, with 155 stages across six different minigames!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Compete against other players from around the world in Rank-Up Challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Use the coins you earn in-game to get plates and titles from the Gotcha! machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Combine plates and titles to create and customize your own Title Plate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・View global leaderboards updated every month in Latest Rankings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Complete a variety of different missions to earn rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*Some minigame stages from THOSE GAMES and THOSE GAMES 2 also appear in this game as tutorial stages.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New players can use these stages to get used to the mechanics before things get too crazy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Or, if you're a THOSE GAMES veteran, skip the tutorial and get right into the extreme action!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Either way, the tutorials will always be there for you, so you can play with confidence!</strong></p>",
